00:27:22,452 --> 00:27:25,163
Aku yakin kau tahu soal itu.

327
00:27:25,247 --> 00:27:27,249
Bagaimana soal
gadis di pesta itu?

328
00:27:27,332 --> 00:27:29,167
- Muridku?
